{"tid":2494134,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"為求催谷打針　林鄭表明檢測可能不再免費","createTime":"2021-04-18T12:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T12:31:52.000Z","uid":261647,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2a099ebae957147b9abd0e270eeceba8db50deb7","tid":2494134,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:19:03.000Z","msg":"https://hk. appledaily. com/local/20210412/MCQNU7XCGFCNHNOOBQUBU36PZ4/<br />\n<br />\n●未來政府或不再提供免費檢測，吸引市民接種疫苗自我保護或得以符合工作要求<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OBQECOJ57ZGIHB2J55ZNNT3K24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOBQECOJ57ZGIHB2J55ZNNT3K24.jpg&h=324aeee0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UTUF4WV44BEXNLDRXG3IFG3O2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUTUF4WV44BEXNLDRXG3IFG3O2A.png&h=38b4c205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭指往後訂立抗疫方針時，將主要考慮有否接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭指，最新的抗疫措施將提供時間表路線圖，包括重開被關處所、避免一刀切式暫停活動，以減低業界影響，以及恢復與外地內地人員往來等，提供多項誘因接種疫苗。林鄭指往後訂立抗疫方針時，將主要考慮有否接種疫苗（完成兩劑及經過14天後）。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又指，考慮停止為市民免費檢測，但須強制檢測的人仍獲免費檢測，並會維持自費檢測服務。她又建議各行業須每隔14天檢測的員工，以接種疫苗代替。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ND2ACA66EBB3BFEMHJHC4WCVAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FND2ACA66EBB3BFEMHJHC4WCVAU.jpg&h=19ca3bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭指，有關抗疫新安排將以完成接種疫苗者為主，故考慮停止免費檢測，但會維持自費檢測服務，以及建議各行業需每隔14天檢測的員工以接種疫苗代替，以便受惠於新抗疫措施。本報記者攝"},{"pid":"ec7318109af87cfbb2789d3d514d849dc76950e7","tid":2494134,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好檢<br />\n又唔好打疫苗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6134fa813835b4c82519117000d4f55086d6f3eb","tid":2494134,"uid":91017,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"D老人家唔L驗, 大爆發"},{"pid":"5eff3dc006671d33ef10c539fc4719f126b47a41","tid":2494134,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec7318109af87cfbb2789d3d514d849dc76950e7","tid":2494134,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:22:42.000Z","msg":"咁咪唔好檢<br />\n又唔好打疫苗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"飲食業唔定期檢測冇得開工麻<br />\n宜家咪即係迫你打一係以後自費驗"},{"pid":"4cb120d4647bc5b8c6ce67f6251c8f9d8d4eff57","tid":2494134,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"打咗針=永世冇可能中肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a03e5846b1f7326fd326c35401b1e3e4181c373","tid":2494134,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cb120d4647bc5b8c6ce67f6251c8f9d8d4eff57","tid":2494134,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"打咗針=永世冇可能中肺炎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:28:00.000Z","msg":"宜家唔係要抗疫<br />\n係要展示你地既服從性呀"},{"pid":"7f0b39a6ec43dac460da7afaa3de0d99b2437d21","tid":2494134,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmakEvwVjBRYXAHGwCsh3JJ1hEFMh5H4GfXgwBtcsU6z8u?filename=9zi7mxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9zi7mxW.jpg&h=54be095a&s={SIZE}\" /